BGU cluster website:
http://frodo.cs.bgu.ac.il/cluster/Main

login to cluster:
ssh username@sge01.bgu.ac.il

submit a cluster bash file:
./demo_submit.sh

Public queues:
all.q; intel_all.q; fairshare.q
Ehud's queue:
ehud.q

some useful cluster functions:

show jobs per user:
qstat -u username

show jobs per queue:
qstat -q ehud.q

delete all submitted jobs:
./delall.sh


